        <section class="characters-hero reveal">
          <p class="eyebrow">138 Generations. 40+ Major Characters.</p>
          <h1>Character Database</h1>
          <p class="lead">
            Meet the carriers, operatives, and antagonists across 3,200 years. Each character
            carries genetic memory from dozens of ancestors, making them simultaneously individuals
            and living archives of human history.
          </p>
        </section>

